{"tid":1479720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員被汽車拖行至死十人被捕","createTime":"2019-08-17T04:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:08:51.000Z","uid":3302,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f54f2913332a840c3c48aaddf1e55dea9df2d72b","tid":1479720,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國一名警員執勤期間，懷疑被汽車拖行至死，至少十人涉嫌謀殺被捕。<br />\n<br />\n鑑證人員去到發現28歲遇害警員哈珀的地點蒐證，案發在南部的伯克郡，哈珀處理一宗爆竊案時遇害，十名介乎13至30歲的男性涉嫌謀殺被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方相信哈珀死前曾經遭汽車拖行，會繼續調查他的死因。入職九年的哈珀四個星期前新婚。<br />\n<br />\n首相約翰遜對案件表示震驚，形容兇徒殘忍，慰問殉職警員家屬。英國政府早前承諾增加一萬個監獄倉位和增聘兩萬警員，加強打擊罪案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=359457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359457&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75Y6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=71c106ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359457&h=523cc28c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=359457</a>"},{"pid":"c72e752f92413119eda99968104d1db914dda4db","tid":1479720,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:24:29.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7ba39f2e2941f10b69ab03d378b0b335e6c1d838","tid":1479720,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"ching 借個位<br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 818注意事項 極重要 銘記於心!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1479618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479618</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手推818啦"},{"pid":"7a1d9226a21523dc7245fd3eb5fbbc2aa8be9fec","tid":1479720,"uid":20721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"dllm一場歡喜一場空"},{"pid":"968e43459cc428c387d0be2